Files included here:

append_if_no_such_line.pp
replace_matching_line.pp
========================
Definitions of the 'append_if_no_such_line' and 'replace_matching_line' functions.

rsyncdconf.pp
=============
Building up an rsyncd.conf file from snippets.

backup_mysql.sh.erb
===================
Example template file showing how to insert passwords into scripts.

secret.rb
=========
Example implementation of the secret function for decrypting private data.

